### ==========================================================================
### BildyApp API — Project Endpoints
### ==========================================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = Bearer TU_ACCESS_TOKEN_AQUI

### ─── Crear un proyecto ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/project
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "client": "SUSTITUIR_POR_CLIENT_ID",
  "name": "Reforma oficinas 3ª planta",
  "projectCode": "PRJ-2026-001",
  "address": {
    "street": "Calle Industria",
    "number": "42",
    "postal": "08025",
    "city": "Barcelona",
    "province": "Barcelona"
  },
  "email": "proyecto@obra.com",
  "notes": "Incluye demolición y montaje de tabiquería"
}

###

### Listar proyectos (paginado + filtros)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/project?page=1&limit=10&sort=-createdAt
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Filtrar por cliente
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/project?client=SUSTITUIR_POR_CLIENT_ID
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Filtrar por nombre y estado activo
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/project?name=Reforma&active=true
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Obtener un proyecto por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/project/SUSTITUIR_POR_ID
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Actualizar un proyecto
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/project/SUSTITUIR_POR_ID
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Reforma oficinas ACTUALIZADA",
  "active": false
}

###

### Archivar un proyecto (soft delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/project/SUSTITUIR_POR_ID?soft=true
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Eliminar un proyecto (hard delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/project/SUSTITUIR_POR_ID
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Listar proyectos archivados
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/project/archived
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Restaurar un proyecto archivado
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/project/SUSTITUIR_POR_ID/restore
Authorization: {{token}}
